import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'

const Pages = () => {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Header/>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<Home />} />
        <Route path="/about" element={<About />} />
        <Route path="/projects" element={<Projects />} />
        <Route path="/services" element={<Services />} />
        <Route path="/plans-and-pricing" element={<Plans />} />
        <Route path="/contact" element={<Contact />} />
        <Route path="/services/book-now" element={<BookNow />} />
        <Route path="services//book-now/fill-form" element={<FillForm />} />
        <Route path="/services/book-now/fill-form/pay-now" element={<PayNow />} />
        <Route path="/plans-and-pricing/select-plan/payment" element={<Payment />} />
      </Routes>
      <Footer/>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default Pages
